txt.en: 'The bog-guardians have chosen to aid us!'
'A bog-guardian! I did not think I would ever see one again!'
'Welcome, friend. The bog-guardians are always welcome!'
'The bog-guardians have come back? I can hardly believe it!'
' Fox friend, there is a new member to the glade. Go and tell the others that they can be trusted as one of our own.'
